beer.beer_description: Three Boys Wheat evokes ancient abbey ales, when yeasts were wild and spices instead of hops were added for bitterness. We use genuine Belgian yeast that with the wheat malt produces the authentic frothy head, cloudiness and huge flavours sought in this wit bier (white beer) style. The addition of coriander and citrus zest really make this beer special.

Born and raised in Dallas, TX and moved to Alaska in 2007. 

Stimulating the Beer economy one pint at a time.
What can I say, I love beer! I only check in a beer once, but I will drink them all until they are gone or I am.
The best beer is the one in your hand.
Beer is proof that God loves us and wants us to be happy! Proud member of the Brew-Tang Clan.
